{"tid":2377980,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣東北部發現「2千萬年前蠕蟲巢穴」 長達2公尺、直徑2.5公分","createTime":"2021-01-24T05:41:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T05:43:12.000Z","uid":1249,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"81ee55882b780ddd17ce1485a74c5f72dbdd5f57","tid":2377980,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:41:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/neHdyK4Y6Cv7klxm.KBGjQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTMzNy4xNTYxNzcxNTYxNzcxNA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/fleuQhU45YLjLut2hin1SQ--~B/aD00NTI7dz04NTg7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/ctwant_com_582/91dee94e5181ebe3a3dfd06315c530b6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FneHdyK4Y6Cv7klxm.KBGjQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTMzNy4xNTYxNzcxNTYxNzcxNA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FfleuQhU45YLjLut2hin1SQ--~B%2FaD00NTI7dz04NTg7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fctwant_com_582%2F91dee94e5181ebe3a3dfd06315c530b6&h=e064f77c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣大學古生物學家在台灣東北部發現距今2000萬年前的巨大蠕蟲巢穴，藉由重建痕跡化石（遠古生物活動所留下的痕跡）後，推估巢穴長達6.5英尺（約2公尺），直徑約1英寸（約2.5公分）左右。這種蠕蟲大約在2000萬年前生活在海底，會撲向毫無防備的海洋生物。<br />\n<br />\n根據《CNN》報導，這種肉食性動物被稱為「博比特蟲」，或稱「沙紋蟲」（Eunice aphroditois），是一種水生捕食性鬃毛蟲，體長從4英寸（約10公分）到10英尺（約3公尺）不等，主要棲息在太平洋海底狹長的洞穴之中。這個6.5英尺長的洞穴曾是牠們的家園，牠們會從海底浮出水面，伏擊海洋生物，並將海洋生物活生生地拖入其巢穴。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rcg_96D9JRAJtT63Arwl3Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM1OS4zODQ2MTUzODQ2MTUzNg--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/pu6V2x94OAPuNDZugN1Qrw--~B/aD00Mzg7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/ctwant_com_582/ff8e15e31a01c19b4b61c28c21fa52a0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Frcg_96D9JRAJtT63Arwl3Q--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM1OS4zODQ2MTUzODQ2MTUzNg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fpu6V2x94OAPuNDZugN1Qrw--~B%2FaD00Mzg7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fctwant_com_582%2Fff8e15e31a01c19b4b61c28c21fa52a0&h=964e8237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n研究人員在洞穴頂部部分發現了高濃度的鐵，認為該蠕蟲可能分泌了黏液來加固洞穴壁面。他們也推測「大約2000萬年前，在歐亞大陸的東南邊界，古老的博比特蠕蟲在海底殖民，埋伏著等待路過的食物」，當獵物靠近蠕蟲時，牠就會從洞穴中爆發出來，抓住獵物並將其拖入洞穴中享用。在海底下，絕望的獵物奮力逃竄，導致洞穴口周圍的沉積物進一步受到干擾。<br />\n<br />\n專家表示，他們假設在2000萬年之前，有隻蠕蟲正埋伏在海底等待進食，這篇研究目前已刊登在《科學報告》（Scientific Report）中。"},{"pid":"c3bd0b5923a0aaa34ea130322ad1aaaa90cd42b2","tid":2377980,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/adSowJG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FadSowJG.jpg&h=7e9e5cc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tMUNYoM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtMUNYoM.jpg&h=0879526d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m9NDkCb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm9NDkCb.jpg&h=0d60c56d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xZt7dXi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxZt7dXi.jpg&h=4762501c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}